/Gervasoni/Hospitality%20Contract/Gervasoni%20Projects%2002.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Projects brochure</a> l <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"http://www.imoderni.com/search.php?manf_id=5&amp;search_x=39&amp;search_y=18&amp;&amp;&amp;from_index_page=yes&amp;pagesize=All\" target=\"_blank\">Link to Gervasoni products on the imoderni web site</a> where you can check prices and download high resolution images for your boards.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Established in 1882 in Udine, Italy, the company originally manufactured wicker goods and its products were featured on early cruise ships. Today, this highly functional collection of beautiful and naturally warm products also grace the finest residences, and hotels and resorts worldwide.\r\nIn three main groups of high quality, casual furniture, Art Director <strong>Paola Navone</strong> fuses modernized production techniques and commercial functionality with the tactile qualities of natural materials and the artistic values of differing cultures.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Indoor</strong> features the <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"http://www.imoderni.com/search.php?manf_id=5&amp;search_x=24&amp;search_y=16&amp;collection=Ghost&amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;from_index_page=yes&amp;pagesize=All\" target=\"_blank\">Ghost</a>, <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"http://www.imoderni.com/search.php?manf_id=5&amp;search_x=26&amp;search_y=19&amp;collection=Gray&amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;from_index_page=yes&amp;pagesize=All\" target=\"_blank\">Gray</a> and <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"http://www.imoderni.com/search.php?manf_id=5&amp;search_x=28&amp;search_y=15&amp;collection=Sweet&amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;from_index_page=yes&amp;pagesize=All\" target=\"_blank\">Sweet</a> collections, plus special compliments. These collections feature slip‐covered upholstery, wooden dining tables and chairs, beds, shelving, credenzas, and coffee tables. Materials include American Walnut, Bamboo, Rawhide &amp; Oak, Slate, Carrara, Metal &amp; China</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Outdoor</strong> features the <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"http://www.imoderni.com/search.php?manf_id=5&amp;search_x=18&amp;search_y=14&amp;collection=Inout&amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;from_index_page=yes&amp;pagesize=All\" target=\"_blank\">InOut</a> collection which integrates materials such as ceramic, stone, wicker, teak and oak, aluminum, the finest quality polyethylene weave and PVC and technology materials such as thermo-treated Ash.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Veranda</strong> or indoor wicker features the <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"http://www.imoderni.com/search.php?&amp;search_x=31&amp;search_y=22&amp;collection=Black&amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;from_index_page=yes&amp;pagesize=All\" target=\"_blank\">Black</a>, and <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"http://www.imoderni.com/search.php?manf_id=5&amp;search_x=27&amp;search_y=11&amp;collection=Croco&amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;from_index_page=yes&amp;pagesize=All\" target=\"_blank\">Croco</a> collections and numerous individual and iconic designs such as Bolla lamp and the Corallo coat stand. These products are hand‐woven on wooden frames using traditional materials such as wicker, bamboo, rawhide, and black pulut.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Using Gervasoni products, entire residential projects can be furnished in particular style. Gervasoni also produces products for contract applications around the world. Images, a list of credits and references are available upon request. Contact <strong>Tammy Paulino</strong> at <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"mailto:tammy@imoderni.com\">tammy@imoderni.com</a> or at (305) 865.8577 for further information.</p>','Gervasoni is the modern standard for upscale, modern, casual furniture from Italy.','','publish','o