chure</a> l <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"http://www.imoderni.com/downloads/Gervasoni/Hospitality%20Contract/Gervasoni%20contract%20products.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Contract brochure</a> l<a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/99568579/Gervasoni%20Installation%20images.pdf\">Installation Images</a> l <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/99568579/Gervasoni%202013%20Pricelist.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">US \"List\" Price List</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"http://www.imoderni.com/search.php?manf_id=5&amp;search_x=39&amp;search_y=18&amp;&amp;&amp;from_index_page=yes&amp;pagesize=All\" target=\"_blank\">Link to all Gervasoni products on the imoderni web site</a> where you can download high resolution images for your boards.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Contact imoderni at the show:\r\n<strong>Moira Stephens</strong>, Sales Manager. <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"mailto:moira@imoderni.com\">moira@imoderni.com</a>: mobile - 786.763.5221\r\n<strong>Armando Aragon</strong>, Market Development Team Manager.<a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"mailto:armando@imoderni.com\">armando@imoderni.com</a>: mobile - 305.926.0287</p>','Michele Tabat invites you to relax with Gervasoni','','publish','open','closed','','michele-tabat-invites-you-to-relax-with-gervasoni','','','2014-08-29 07:47:10','2014-08-29 07:47:10','',0,'http://dev.tenthmatrix.co.uk:8088/imoderni/blog/?p=37',0,'post','',2),(38,1,'2014-08-29 07:47:07','2014-08-29 07:47:07','','instltion','','inherit','open','open','','instltion','','','2014-08-29 07:47:07','2014-08-29 07:47:07','',37,'http://dev.tenthmatrix.co.uk:8088/imoderni/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/instltion.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(39,1,'2014-08-29 07:47:10','2014-08-29 07:47:10','<b style=\"color: #000000;\">Michele Tabat invites you to relax with Gervasoni</b><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span><