as gradually expanded to now include multiple varaitions of armchairs, dining chairs, sectional systems, ottomans (floor and back rest), love seats,  sofas. Beds are also available in variations of style and size, including a sofa and trundle bed.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Gervasoni Ghost is in use worldwide in upscale hospitality contract and residential locations and has been specified by many of the world’s top interior design firms.</p>\r\n&nbsp;',' For the First Time, Indoor Comfort Outdoors!','','inherit','open','open','','40-revision-v1','','','2014-08-29 07:48:45','2014-08-29 07:48:45','',40,'http://dev.tenthmatrix.co.uk:8088/imoderni/blog/?p=42',0,'revision','',0),(45,1,'2014-08-29 12:34:58','2014-08-29 12:34:58','<b style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-41\" src=\"http://dev.tenthmatrix.co.uk:8088/imoderni/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />For the First Time, Indoor Comfort Outdoors!</b><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span><br style=\"color: #000000;\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Posted On: 2014-03-20 </span>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><i>For Release March 28, 2014</i></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">After two years in development, Ghost, Gervasoni’s most successful casual relaxed furniture collection, has now been realized for outdoor use. First available products include a collection of sofas &amp; armchairs, with customization available for dining chairs and a sectional system. For the first time, hospitality contract and residential designers can choose to ignore the commercial aluminum and plastics systems that have dominated the outdoor furniture market in recent years. Visually identical to the indoor collection, Ghost for outdoor seating is modern, comfortable, and as attractive as its indoor counterpart. Once again, Gervasoni leads the casual relaxed furniture market!</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\