 residential locations and has been specified by many of the world’s top interior design firms.</p>\r\n&nbsp;',' For the First Time, Indoor Comfort Outdoors!','','inherit','open','open','','40-revision-v1','','','2014-09-01 10:27:14','2014-09-01 10:27:14','',40,'http://dev.tenthmatrix.co.uk:8088/imoderni/blog/?p=58',0,'revision','',0),(62,1,'2014-09-02 05:25:39','2014-09-02 05:25:39','<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Hospitality &amp; Commercial Spaces, Gardens, Living Rooms, Dining Rooms, Bedrooms and now even Bathrooms!</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Indoor and outdoor spaces, commercial or residential, Wall &amp; Deco Art for Walls will transform your world! Contact<strong>Tammy Paulino</strong>: (305) 865.8577 or <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"mailto:tammy@imoderni.com\">tammy@imoderni.com</a> to find out how to get a free digital rendering for your next space design. Wall &amp; Deco is not your Parent\'s Wallpaper!</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"http://www.wallanddeco.com/News.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">See Wall &amp; Deco News</a></p>\r\n<br style=\"color: #000000;\" /><br style=\"color: #000000;\" />\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Download: <a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/99568579/Wall%20%26%20Deco%202013%20brochure.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">2013 Indoor Brochure</a>/<a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/99568579/Wall%20%26%20Deco%20outdoor%20brochure.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">2013 Outdoor Brochure</a>/<a style=\"color: #110975;\" href=\"https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/99568579/Wall%20%26%20Deco%20four%20page%20introduction.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">4  .... </a></p>','Walls that rock worlds! ','','publish','open','closed','','walls-that-rock-worlds','','','2014-09-02 10:36:33','2014-09-02 10:36:33','',0,'http://dev.tenthmatrix.co.uk:8088/imoderni/blog/?p=62',0,'post','',0),(63,1,'2014-09-02 05:13:06','2014-09-02 05:13:06','','Walls th