se\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:573:\"<p>Tv Series Tweet, recent tweets by the most popular tv series! TvSeriesTweet is the new app for smartphones and tablets: Follow the best and recent tweets from the best tv series You don&#8217;t even need a personal Twitter account More emphasis on words &#38; images (retweets &#38; replies are cut) ◄ Always fresh ► View the most [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/\">Tv Series Tweet &#8211; follow them with your phone!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it\">WhileTrue</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WhileTrue\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4387:\"<p><a href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/icon_128.png\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-624\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/icon_128.png\" alt=\"TvSeriesTweet logo\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\" /></a><em><strong>Tv Series Tweet</strong>, recent tweets by the most popular tv series!</em> TvSeriesTweet is the new app for smartphones and tablets:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Follow the best and recent tweets from the best tv series</li>\n<li>You don&#8217;t even need a personal Twitter account</li>\n<li>More emphasis on words &amp; images (retweets &amp; replies are cut)</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=it.whiletrue.tvseriestweet\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://developer.android.com/images/brand/en_app_rgb_wo_60.png\" alt=\"Android app on Google Play\" /></a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"https://marketplace.firefox.com/app/polistweet/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://marketplace.cdn.mozilla.net/media/img/mkt/badges/firefox-marketplace_badge-black_172_60.png?b=552b1c2-530f8025\" alt=\"Firefox OS app\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><a href=\"http://windowsphone.com/s?appId=c86047da-e927-4e51-b96c-24b7998a7440\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/154x40_WPS_Download_blk.png\" alt=\"download from Windows Phone Store\" /></a></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>◄ Always fresh ►</p>\n<ul>\n<li>View the most shared recent tweets, along with their shares count.</li>\n<li>Touch a tweet to instantly share it with your contacts.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span id=\"more-617\"></span>◄ Update &amp; Focus ►</p>\n<ul>\n<li>View and select the list of the leading and most active Tv Series on Twitter</li>\n<li>See the series actual influence value (changes day by day)</li>\n<li>Touch the Tv Series to read its best tweets, turn it off to hide its tweets.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<a href=\'http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/tvseriestweet_screenshot2/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/tvseriestweet_screenshot2-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail colorbox-617 \" alt=\"tv series tweet\" /></a>\n<a href=\'http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/screen/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/screen-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail colorbox-617 \" alt=\"TvSeriesTweet\" /></a>\n<a href=\'http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/tvseriestweet_screenshot1/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/tvseriestweet_screenshot1-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail colorbox-617 \" alt=\"TvSeriesTweet on smartphone\" /></a>\n<a href=\'http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/tvseriestweet_screenshot3/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/tvseriestweet_screenshot3-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail colorbox-617 \" alt=\"TvSeriesTweet on tablet\" /></a>\n\n<p>◄ Follow the Trend ► View the best hashtags and the most used words on Twitter by Tv Series accounts</p>\n<p>◄ Lots of Tv Series ► Featuring the best Tv Series, including: House of Cards, Game Of Thrones, Da Vinci&#8217;s Demons, Cosmos, How I met your mother, The Big Bang Theory, Hannibal, Orange Is the New Black, The Following, Helix, Teen Wolf, Scandal, Once: Wonderland, The Walking Dead, The Tomorrow People, Breaking Bad, 2 Broke Girls, Under The Dome, Black Sails, Brooklyn Nine-Nine, Almost Human, Masters of Sex, True Detective, The Killing, American Horror Story, Awkward, Glee, Pretty Little Liars, The Vampire Diaries, Falling Skies, True Blood etc.</p>\n<h3>Technical info</h3>\n<p>The app is made using HTML5 + Javascript and compiled with Cordova; the code was organized with Backbone (development framework) and the GUI with Ratchet 2.</p>\n<h3>News</h3>\n<p>Release 1.8: explore the positive and negative trends revealed by our sentiment analysis</p>\n<h3>Known bugs</h3>\n<p>Windows Phone users can&#8217;t hide Series, we&#8217;re fixing it within the next updated.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/\">Tv Series Tweet &#8211; follow them with your phone!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it\">WhileTrue</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Fruitbots, a JS bot challenge\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/fruitbots-js-bot-challenge/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/fruitbots-js-bot-challenge/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 18 Dec 2013 15:19:48 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"bot challenge\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"fruitbots\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"javascript\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"scribd\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/?p=506\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:554:\"<p>I sometimes like to join bot challenges to improve my programming skills and logic reasoning. Last week I discovered Fruitbots, a JavaScript bot challenge created by the Scribd staff. Like every good challenge of its type, it features simple rules and a clear bot API, also it can be scripted in 4 languages: Python, Lua, Ruby [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/fruitbots-js-bot-challenge/\">Fruitbots, a JS bot challenge</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it\">WhileTrue</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WhileTrue\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1906:\"<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-508 alignright\" alt=\"Fruitbots challenge\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/fruitbots.png\" width=\"304\" height=\"377\" />I sometimes like to join <strong>bot challenges</strong> to improve my programming skills and logic reasoning.</p>\n<p>Last week I discovered <a title=\"Fruitbots\" href=\"http://fruitbots.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Fruitbots</strong></a>, a JavaScript bot challenge created by the Scribd staff. Like every good challenge of its type, it features simple rules and a clear bot API, also it can be scripted in 4 languages: Python, Lua, Ruby and JavaScript.</p>\n<p>The <strong>Fruitbots world</strong> is a board with different kind of fruits lying around. The goal is to collect more fruits than the opponent bot, of many types as possible.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-506\"></span>At the moment I developed just a simple-sample JavaScript bot called<strong> Look a Lot</strong>, with a clean strategy:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>If on a <em>useful fruit</em>, eat it!</li>\n<li>Else, go to the <em>best direction</em>, looking at:\n<ul>\n<li>nearer and rarer fruits</li>\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\">bonus for disputed fruits, if nearer than the opponent</span></li>\n<li>avoid previous position, out of the border moves and to PASS</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The bot seems good enough to get into the <strong>Top 50</strong>. If you&#8217;re curious <a title=\"Fruitbots &quot;Look a Lot&quot;\" href=\"https://github.com/formikaio/Fruitbots_Look-a-Lot\" target=\"_blank\">the code is here</a>, but if you like programming I invite you first to <strong>join the challenge</strong> and find your preferred bot rules!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/fruitbots-js-bot-challenge/\">Fruitbots, a JS bot challenge</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it\">WhileTrue</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/fruitbots-js-bot-challenge/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"Categorized Tag Cloud widget for WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/categorized-tag-cloud-widget-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/categorized-tag-cloud-widget-wordpress/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 26 Nov 2013 13:47:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Projects\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"category\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"filter\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"widget\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/?p=489\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:584:\"<p>Categorized Tag Cloud is a free plugin for WordPress, developed by the Whiletrue.it staff to generate a cloud with the website&#8217;s most used tags, in a sidebar widget. The words inside the cloud are filtered by category, so you can better match your content by removing the unnecessary tag ids. Options The following options are [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/categorized-tag-cloud-widget-wordpress/\">Categorized Tag Cloud widget for WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it\">WhileTrue</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WhileTrue\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1604:\"<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-534\" alt=\"categorized tag cloud widget\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/categorized-tag-cloud-widget.png\" width=\"599\" height=\"194\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Categorized Tag Cloud</strong> is a free plugin for WordPress, developed by the Whiletrue.it staff to generate a cloud with the website&#8217;s most used tags, in a sidebar widget.</p>\n<p>The words inside the cloud are <strong>filtered by category</strong>, so you can better match your content by removing the unnecessary tag ids.</p>\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\"><span id=\"more-489\"></span></span></p>\n<h3>Options</h3>\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\">The following options are customizable:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>category filters</li>\n<li>number of tags shown</li>\n<li>tag colors (fixed or random)</li>\n<li>tag hover color</li>\n<li>smallest and biggest font size</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Download</h3>\n<p>Click on the button below to download the plugin from the official WordPress site:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Categorized Tag Cloud plugin\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/plugins/categorized-tag-cloud/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-29\" alt=\"download\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/download.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/categorized-tag-cloud-widget-wordpress/\">Categorized Tag Cloud widget for WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it\">WhileTrue</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/categorized-tag-cloud-widget-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"7\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"2013 Black and white Free WordPress theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/2013-black-and-white-wordpress-theme/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/2013-black-and-white-wordpress-theme/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 18 Oct 2013 08:08:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Projects\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"2013\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"black and white\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"css\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"twenty thirteen\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/?p=429\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:582:\"<p>Do you feel there&#8217;s too much color in the web? Try our brand new 2013 Black and white Free Wordpress theme! It&#8217;s a lightweight child theme of Twenty Thirteen (the default theme for WordPress 3.6), based on several shades of grey for different post formats. The CSS stylesheet aims to be simple to understand and edit to [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/2013-black-and-white-wordpress-theme/\">2013 Black and white Free WordPress theme</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it\">WhileTrue</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WhileTrue\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1495:\"<p><a href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/screenshot.png\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-431 alignright\" alt=\"screenshot\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/screenshot-300x225.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>Do you feel there&#8217;s too much color in the web? Try our brand new <strong>2013 Black and white Free Wordpress theme</strong>!</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a lightweight <strong>child theme of Twenty Thirteen</strong> (the default theme for WordPress 3.6), based on several shades of grey for different post formats.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-429\"></span>The CSS stylesheet aims to be simple to understand and edit to fit your needs. Like our other projects, it&#8217;s released with a GPL license.</p>\n<p><strong>2013 Black and white</strong> is an easy starting point for desaturated websites, try its 50 shades of grey, and more!</p>\n<p>Click here to download it from the official WordPress website:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"2013 Black and white WordPress Theme download\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/themes/2013-black-and-white\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-29\" alt=\"download\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/download.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/2013-black-and-white-wordpress-theme/\">2013 Black and white Free WordPress theme</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it\">WhileTrue</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/2013-black-and-white-wordpress-theme/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"Deploying in 2013, from Grunt to Amazon S3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/deploying-2013-grunt-amazon-s3/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/deploying-2013-grunt-amazon-s3/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 11 Oct 2013 12:51:05 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"amazon s3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"backbone\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"grunt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"nodejs\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/?p=415\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:596:\"<p>What is your deploying chain right now? How has it changed over time? The actual deploy of a single page app I&#8217;m involved is based on a single Grunt script, executing on a Node.js environment. The Grunt chain takes all the files (Backbone.js app, JS libs, HTML templates, CSS and images), checks, copies, concatenates and minificates them. The [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/deploying-2013-grunt-amazon-s3/\">Deploying in 2013, from Grunt to Amazon S3</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it\">WhileTrue</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WhileTrue\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2037:\"<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\">What is your </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\">deploying chain</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\"> right now? How has it changed over time?</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-421\" alt=\"Deploying in 2013\" src=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/deploying_2013.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"166\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\">The actual deploy of a single page app I&#8217;m involved is based on <strong>a single </strong></span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\">Grunt</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\"><strong> script</strong>, executing on a Node.js environment. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\">The Grunt chain takes all the files (</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\">Backbone.js app, JS libs, HTML templates, CSS and images), <strong>checks, copies, concatenates and minificates</strong> them. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\"><span id=\"more-415\"></span>The resulting dir is <strong>versioned and uploaded</strong> to an Amazon S3 bucket and to a redundant static cache. We start with 259 files (images excluded) to end up with 13 files, serving 4 different environments. Every final file is available in debug and minified version, requests can be made with http and https protocols.</span></p>\n<p>Previously, all this was made manually, for 4 different servers. Now, only an error free, time saving, automated single task. Thanks, Grunt!</p>\n<p><em>p.s. If only Amazon S3 would serve gzipped files easily &#8230;</em></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it/deploying-2013-grunt-amazon-s3/\">Deploying in 2013, from Grunt to Amazon S3</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.whiletrue.it\">WhileTrue</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/deploying-2013-grunt-amazon-s3/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:29:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";a:9:{s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Mon, 01 Sep 2014 09:31:44 GMT\";s:6:\"server\";s:6:\"Apache\";s:12:\"x-powered-by\";s:21:\"PHP/5.3.3-7+squeeze14\";s:4:\"vary\";s:22:\"Cookie,Accept-Encoding\";s:10:\"x-pingback\";s:34:\"http://www.whiletrue.it/xmlrpc.php\";s:4:\"etag\";s:34:\"\"a36bf0183d9ac2b85a82800f35490019\"\";