ata\";s:31:\"Tue, 19 Mar 2013 18:36:11 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Plugin Updates\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"http://pinterestplugin.com/?p=3439\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:321:\"The hover &#8220;Pin It&#8221; button part of the plugin has a few new useful features in the latest &#8220;Pin It&#8221; Button Pro 2.2.0 release including: Place the hover button in any of the 4 corners of images. Use any of the 30 included button designs for the hover button. They can be different from your [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Phil Derksen\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2143:\"<p>The hover &#8220;Pin It&#8221; button part of the plugin has a few new useful features in the latest &#8220;Pin It&#8221; Button Pro 2.2.0 release including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 13px;\">Place the hover button in any of the 4 corners of images.</span></li>\n<li>Use any of the 30 included button designs for the hover button. They can be different from your page-level &#8220;Pin It&#8221; button.</li>\n<li>Upload or select your own custom button for the hover button AND the page-level button.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Here&#8217;s a screenshot of the new settings:</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-3440\" alt=\"pin it button image hover and custom button upload settings\" src=\"http://cdn.pinplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/pin-it-button-image-hover-and-custom-button-upload-settings-2013-03-19.png\" width=\"485\" height=\"378\" data-pin-url=\"http://pinplugins.com/hover-pin-it-button-features-added/\" /></p>\n<p>Plugin customers have spoken, and these were a few of the top requested features and took priority. But more is always under development.</p>\n<p><a title=\"Pinterest “Pin It” Button Pro WordPress Plugin\" href=\"http://pinplugins.com/\">Click here to purchase &#8220;Pin It&#8221; Button Pro</a> (if you don&#8217;t already have it) and get these fantastic features now!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Article\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<meta itemprop=\"url\" content=\"http://pinplugins.com/hover-pin-it-button-features-added/\" />\n<meta itemprop=\"name\" content=\"Hover &#8220;Pin It&#8221; Button Features Added\" />\n<meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"The hover &#8220;Pin It&#8221; button part of the plugin has a few new useful features in the latest &#8220;Pin It&#8221; Button Pro 2.2.0 release including: Place the hover button in any of the 4 corners of images. Use any of the 30 included button designs for the hover button. They can be different from your ...\" />\n<meta itemprop=\"author\" content=\"Phil Derksen\" />\n<meta itemprop=\"datePublished\" content=\"2013-03-19\" />\n<meta itemprop=\"wordCount\" content=\"145\" />\n<meta itemprop=\"articleSection\" content=\"Plugin Updates\" />\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"http://pinplugins.com/hover-pin-it-button-features-added/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://pur